LDG_INIT(3)                   LDG Call                     LDG_INIT(3)

NAME
   ldg_init - LDG interface of a library.

SYNOPSIS
   int ldg_init( LDGLIB *ldg);

PARAMETERS
      ldg    : adress of the LDGLIB structure,
      return : 0 no error. -1: the library was launched by a non
               LDG application.

DESCRIPTION
    This function provides the  interface between the LDG-library  and
    the LDG-system.

